                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/climate-negotiator-previews-chinas-approach-un-climate-summit">Climate negotiator previews China&#039;s approach to UN Climate Summit</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/Xie_Zhenhua_2014_0.jpg" alt="" title="" width="90" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
