  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>China&#8217;s chief climate negotiator, Xie Zhenhua, held a press conference Friday and made statements that may preview China&#8217;s approach to the UN Climate Summit on September 23rd.</p>

<p><a href="http://af.reuters.com/article/energyOilNews/idAFL3N0RK1XW20140919?sp=true">Read more&#8230;</a></p></div>
