<p>Over the past two decades, the world has witnessed a remarkable period of economic and human development: More than 2 billion people <a href="http://www.un.org/millenniumgoals/pdf/MDG%20Report%202012.pdf">have gained access</a> to improved drinking water; life expectancy <a href="http://www.healthmetricsandevaluation.org/gbd/publications/healthy-life-expectancy-187-countries-1990-2010-systematic-analysis-global-bu">has increased</a> by approximately five years; more children are going to s</p></div>
