  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/op-ed-blinded-solar-light">Op-Ed: Blinded by the (solar) light</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-library-file-fid">
                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p><IMG align="left" hspace="15" src="../files/chinainfo/imagefield_thumbs/Kelly_Gallagher_0.jpg?1312399709" />&#8220;The Obama Administration‚Äôs preliminary decision to impose a 31 per cent tariff on solar panels imported from China is short sighted. The move could cause a trade war, hurt the US economy, jeopardize US security interests, and put the world further off course in terms of meeting its global climate change goals.&#8221;</p>

<p><a href="http://blogs.ft.com/beyond-brics/2012/05/22/guest-post-blinded-by-the-solar-light/?catid=491&amp;SID=google#axzz1vhhMeBo3">Read the full article at the Financial Times&#8230;</a></p></div>
