                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/what-shale-gas-china-means-united-states">What Shale Gas In China Means For The United States</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/ShaleGas.jpg" alt="" title="" width="139" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
