  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>Today I testified before the U.S.-China Economic and Security Review Commission during a <a href="http://www.uscc.gov/hearings/2012hearings/written_testimonies/hr12_01_26.php">hearing</a> on <em>China‚Äôs Global Quest for Resources and Implications for the United States</em>. In <a href="../library/testimony-sarah-forbes-us-china-economic-and-security-review-commission-january-26-2012">my testimony</a>, I described the prospects for shale gas in China and its implications for the United States.</p></div>
