                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>The draft of China‚Äôs much-anticipated 12th Five-Year Plan was released this Saturday, March 5 at the opening session of the National People‚Äôs Congress (NPC).  The Plan will actually be brought to a vote at the close of the session later this week. While there may be some changes to the Plan, in past years these have not been large.</p></div>
