  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>Indian Environment Minister Jairam Ramesh described the ‚ÄúCopenhagen Spirit‚Äù as substantially improving ties between China and India and leading to improved cooperation in related environmental areas, including hydrographic data, glaciological research and forestry.  He expressed hope that an MOU signed last fall on energy technologies would yield some concrete projects, but admitted those opportunities had yet to be explored.</p></div>
