  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>China‚Äôs policies to prioritize, fund and deploy clean technology R&amp;D and innovation over the short and medium term stem from an ambition to emerge as a global power in science and technology through clean technology R&amp;D and innovation.</p></div>
